@node Main "Midnight Blanker Document"

  Those flying creatures are up to trouble again.  Well you wouldn't

  want to fix your morning breakfast with these guys but you might

  start the day out with them.  These little toilets were drawn

  by myself, (I'm NO artist) so if you would like to see better

  artwork send me your toilets!


